node.text:
Which of these vibrant birds is your favorite? 1-10? 🦜🎨Apply for a feature following the link in our bio and we will publish your photos in our account: @tourfervor

Names and Photos:
1) Silver throated Tanager - @jeffreypatrickkarnes
2) European Starling - @raheel.aazim
3) Mandarin duck - @eccentricwildlife
4) Golden-tailed Sapphire - @birddetective
5) Strawberry Finch - @praharsha_wildlife_stories
6) Periquito-rico - @macrotake
7) European Bee-eater - @dorugroza
8) Pink Robin - @ravi_arora
9) Keel billed Toucan - @floriankusterwildlife
10) Oriental Dwarf Kingfisher - @rahul_belsare
